Steps to run the project

Install dependencies:

cd client && npm install (or yarn install) && npm audit fix --force && npm install react-scripts@latest webpack@latest
cd server && npm install (or yarn install) && npm audit fix --force
cd socket && npm install (or yarn install) && npm audit fix --force


Start servers:

cd server && npm start (or node index.js if no start script)
cd client && ng serve (or npm start)
cd socket && node index.js

